### Health check
GET http://localhost:5000/

### Get all tuitions
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tuitions

### Get single tuition (replace with real id)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tuitions/6578a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0

### Get tuitions by student email
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tuitions/student/test@gmail.com

### Create JWT token
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/jwt
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@test.com"
}

### Get user by email
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/test@gmail.com

### Create new user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "newuser@test.com",
    "displayName": "Test User",
    "role": "student"
}

### Get all users (admin)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users

### Post new tuition
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tuitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "subject": "Mathematics",
    "class_name": "Class 10",
    "location": "Dhanmondi, Dhaka",
    "salary": 5000,
    "student_email": "student@test.com",
    "days_per_week": 4
}

### Get applications for a tuition
GET http://localhost:5000/api/applications/tuition/6578a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0

### Submit application (tutor)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tuitionId": "6578a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0",
    "tutorId": "6578a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d1",
    "tutorEmail": "tutor@test.com",
    "tutorName": "Test Tutor",
    "qualifications": "BSc in Mathematics",
    "experience": "2 years",
    "expectedSalary": 6000
}
